Detailed Description

cvmx_uahc::_ehci_usbsts

USBSTS = USB Status Register This register indicates pending interrupts and various states of the Host Controller. The status resulting from a transaction on the serial bus is not indicated in this register. Software sets a bit to 0 in this register by writing a 1 to it.
